# Support - My QuizApp

## Contact Us
If you need help or have questions about My QuizApp, please contact us:

**Email**: f.mehmetkural@gmail.com

## Frequently Asked Questions

### How do I use the app?
1. Select a quiz type (Multiple Choice or Norm Questions)
2. Answer the questions
3. Your score is saved automatically on your device

### How do I reset my score?
Tap the "Reset Score" button in the quiz screen.

### The app is not working properly
Please send us an email with:
- Device model (e.g., iPhone 14)
- iOS version (e.g., iOS 17.2)
- Description of the problem

### Feature Requests
We'd love to hear your ideas! Email us at:  f.mehmetkural@gmail.com

## Privacy
We do not collect any personal data. All quiz progress is stored locally on your device.

